## вљ™пёЏ Configuration

All training parameters live in `configs/config.yaml`:

```yaml
root_dir: "/data"
experiment_name: "plant_disease_classification_resnet50"

dataset:
  name: "PlantVillage"
  num_classes: 15
  test_size: 0.1
  val_size: 0.1

train:
  freeze_backbone: true
  epochs: 20
  batch_size: 64
  learning_rate: 0.0003
  unfreeze_backbone_epoch: 10
```

---

## рџ§  Model Architecture

Transfer learning on **ResNet50** pretrained on ImageNet:

```
ResNet50 (backbone)
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ Frozen for first 10 epochs
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ Fine-tuned from epoch 10 onward

Custom Classifier Head:
    Linear(2048 в†’ 512)
    ReLU
    Dropout(0.5)
    Linear(512 в†’ 15)
```

**Training strategy:**
- Phase 1 (epochs 1вЂ“10): Only the classification head is trained; backbone is frozen.
- Phase 2 (epochs 11вЂ“20): Full model is fine-tuned end-to-end with a low learning rate.



## рџ“¦ MLflow Tracking

Every training run automatically logs:

| Category | Details |
|----------|---------|
| **Parameters** | learning rate, batch size, optimizer, epochs, freeze strategy |
| **Metrics** | train/val loss & accuracy per epoch, best val accuracy, best epoch |
| **Artifacts** | loss curves, accuracy curves, confusion matrix |
| **Model** | registered to MLflow Model Registry as `PlantDisease@champion` |

